    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification demonstrates predictions within combined uncertainty bounds across the COU operating envelope. The assessment team concluded that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support the hemolysis acceptance decision for the Class III VAD device.",
